@startuml 攻击验证与风险复现时序图

skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam participantFontSize 13
skinparam noteFontSize 11

actor 用户 as User
participant "前端页面" as Frontend
participant "AttackController" as AC
participant "PoisonGenerator" as PG
participant "KnowledgeInjector" as KI
participant "AttackEvaluator" as AE

User -> Frontend : 填写攻击参数并提交
Frontend -> AC : create_task(config)
AC -> AC : 创建AttackTask实例
AC --> Frontend : 返回 task_id

User -> Frontend : 点击执行攻击任务
Frontend -> AC : start_task(task_id)
AC -> PG : generate_poison_docs(task)
PG -> PG : BOGA-RAGP算法生成毒化文本
PG --> AC : 返回 List[PoisonDoc]
AC -> KI : inject_documents(poison_docs, kb_id)
KI -> KI : 写入知识库并刷新向量索引
KI --> AC : 返回注入结果
AC -> AE : evaluate_attack(task_id)
AE -> AE : 计算ASR和RSR
AE --> AC : 返回评估结果
AC --> Frontend : 返回执行结果(ASR, RSR)
Frontend --> User : 展示攻击完成状态及效果指标

@enduml
